# Purpose: Directory placeholder for session transcripts and receipts
# ================================================================================
#
# Description:
#     This directory stores session transcripts and SessionReceipts generated
#     during chat sessions. These files are gitignored and contain sensitive
#     session data.
#
# Expected Files:
#     - session_YYYYMMDD_HHMMSS.txt: Session transcript files
#     - session_YYYYMMDD_HHMMSS_receipt.json: SessionReceipt JSON files
#
# Transcript Format:
#     seqno | timestamp | ciphertext | signature | peer-cert-fingerprint
#
# SessionReceipt Format (JSON):
#     {
#         "type": "receipt",
#         "peer": "client|server",
#         "first_seq": 1,
#         "last_seq": 10,
#         "transcript_sha256": "hex_hash",
#         "sig": "base64_rsa_signature"
#     }
#
# Links to Other Files:
#     - app/storage/transcript.py: Generates transcript and receipt files
#     - app/client.py: Creates client-side transcripts
#     - app/server.py: Creates server-side transcripts
#     - .gitignore: This directory is gitignored
#     - tests/manual/NOTES.md: Referenced in testing procedures
#
# Result:
#     - Provides storage for session transcripts
#     - Enables non-repudiation evidence
#     - Allows offline verification of sessions
#     - Prevents accidental commit of sensitive session data
#
